text: Nimisha is an Indian name. It may refer to: *Nimisha Madhvani, Ugandan diplomat. *Nimisha Mehta, British actress. *Nimisha Mukerji, Canadian director . *Nimisha Pandey, Indian director. *Nimisha Sajayan, Indian actress. *Nimisha Suresh, Indian actress. *Nimisha Vakharia, Indian actress.
